  "title": "Food Production Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are from central kitchen in food manufacturing sector located in Singapore, fostering a positive work environment—\"Work Hard, Play Hard!\" We're looking for passionate management professionals to join our family!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Position:</strong> Production Manager</p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> From $3,600 onwards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the entire food production process to ensure efficiency, quality, and compliance with safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>Develop and implement production plans, schedules, and cost-control strategies to optimize output.</li>\n  <li>Lead and manage production teams, providing training, guidance, and performance evaluations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with food safety standards, HACCP, GMP, and regulatory requirements.</li>\n  <li>Monitor equipment maintenance and coordinate with the maintenance team to minimize downtime.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with procurement and inventory teams to ensure adequate raw materials and packaging supplies.</li>\n  <li>Identify process improvements and implement new technologies to enhance productivity.</li>\n  <li>Analyze production data and generate reports to inform business decisions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong leadership and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Experience with production planning, budgeting, and process optimization.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and meet production deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Positive work attitude and a strong team player</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ 20 days of paid leave</p>\n<p>✔ Medical benefits &amp; insurance coverage</p>\n<p>✔ Various allowances &amp; incentives (Meal allowances, Revenue Incentives, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Various bonuses (AWS, performance, attendance)</p>\n<p>✔ Various rewards (Best Employee Award, Long services award, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Strong career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>✔ Revenue incentives</p>\n<p>✔ Sponsored courses for career growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you’re the right fit for our team, send your application here! We look forward to your application!</strong></p>",
